u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEST-TEXEDITORS:Thisi     03-03 0012
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEST-TEX </SLUG>
 EDITORS: This is a test from the Fort Worth
Star-Telegram. nn
<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-03-03-99 0114EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990303.0039 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-03 01:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5525 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-REEVES-COLUMN-TEX     03-03 0877
