<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-03 13:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6089 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CUSTODY-BATTLE-BOS &LR;      03-03 1486
