<DOCNO> NYT19990303.0198 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-03 13:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6144 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FOOD-JONES-2TAKES-BOS     03-03 1042
