themselves into a city, called Leisure Woods, population 18,000,
all over 55. By Don Terry.
</P>
<P>
   MAINE-FOREST (Boston) _ In what is described as the largest land
protection deal ever, a family has agreed to sell development
rights to 800,000 acres of Maine forest to forest association. By
Carey Goldberg.
</P>
<P>
   With map.
