   AUTO-SALES (Detroit) _ General Motors' sales rose 18 percent
last month, to 382,261, well above estimates of a 6.4 percent
increase. For the industry over all, February sales amounted to
14.6 million units, analysts estimate, up from 13.4 million units
in January. By Michelle Krebs.
</P>
