<P>
   WINSTON-ADDITIVES (Undated) _ RJR Nabisco Holdings reaches a
settlement with the FTC under which it will add a disclaimer to
Winston ads that will say the cigarettes are not safer just because
they contain ``no additives.'' By Constance L. Hays.
</P>
