<P>
   MARKET (New York) _ At midday, the industrial average was down
26 points, or 0.3 1 percent, and the Nasdaq index was down 13
points, or 0.6 percent. Elsewhere, prices rose 1.8 percent in Tokyo
and closed little changed in Hong Kong. They decreased 2.7 percent
in Frankfurt, 0.3 percent in London, and 0.4 percent in Mexico.
They were flat in Brazil. On the American debt market, the long
bond was off 21/32 point, with the yield at 5.66 percent. By Robert
D. Hershey.
