Committee. By Bernard Weinraub.
</P>
<P>
   BOOK-TALK (Undated) _ The weekly book column. By Martin Arnold.
</P>
<P>
   TAXES-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``The Greedy Hand: How Taxes Drive
Honest Americans Crazy and What To Do About It,'' by Amity Shlaes
(Random House). Reviewed by Christopher Lehmann-Haupt.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS &LR;  (``s'' code)
</P>
<P>
   BKC-RHODEN-COLUMN (Undated) _ Sports of The Times column on
Leonard Hamilton, coach of the very surprising, and very good,
Miami basketball team. By William C. Rhoden.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-BERKOW-COLUMN (Undated) _ Sports of The Times column on
78-year-old Fuzzy Levane, the son of an Italian classical musician
who has spent a lifetime in basketball as a player, coach and scout
and who will be honored in New York on March 14. By Ira Berkow.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-BIGEAST (New York) _ Action at the Big East men's
tournament. By Joe Drape.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-DEVILS-MAPLELEAFS (Toronto) _ N.J. Devils at Toronto, 7:30
p.m. ET start. By Alex Yannis.
</P>
<P>
   OLY-U.S. (Washington) _ The USOC responds to the criticism it
received from the Mitchell commission earlier this week. The
commission says the USOC was glaringly lax in overseeing Salt Lake
City's bid for the Winter Olympics; the USOC says that isn't the
case. By Richard Sandomir.
</P>
