<P>
   &UR; Top Ten Ways Y2K Will Affect Disney World &LR;
</P>
<P>
   10.Accidental switch back to 19,000 Leagues Under the Sea.
</P>
<P>
   9.Screwed up computers report EuroDisney turning a profit.
