   STATE LEGISLATIVE NEWS
</P>
<P>
   TEX-LEGIS-RYLANDERREVIEW _ Comptroller Carole Keeton Rylander,
who took office eight weeks ago, rushed to update the Texas
Performance Review left by her Democratic predecessor. On
Wednesday, she releases her recommendations for cost savings and
efficiency in state government. But with the bill-filing deadline
less than two weeks away, is it too late? (Elizondo, Austin
American-Statesman).
</P>
