as a strong indication that Hillary Rodham Clinton will run for the
Senate from New York, the first lady proclaims her committment to
government and politics before some of her most passionate
supporters, New York Democratic women, in a packed and enthusiastic
ballroom of the Plaza Hotel. By Elisabeth Bumiller. (Scheduled to
