</P>
<P>
   4. ``Crossing Brooklyn Ferry'' (poem)
</P>
<P>
   5. ``Fargo'' (screenplay)
</P>
<P>
   6. ``Fort Worth'' (novel)
</P>
<P>
   7. ``The Happy Journey From Camden to Trenton'' (one-act play)
</P>
<P>
   8. ``Living in Little Rock With Miss Little Rock'' (novel)
</P>
<P>
   9. ``Meet Me in St. Louis'' (connected stories)
</P>
<P>
   10. ``The Mysteries of Pittsburgh'' (novel)
</P>
<P>
   11. ``Nashville'' (screenplay)
</P>
<P>
   12. ``Old New York'' (four novellas)
</P>
<P>
   13. ``The Philadelphia Story'' (play)
</P>
<P>
   14. ``San Francisco'' (screenplay)
</P>
<P>
   15. ``A Summons to Memphis'' (novel)
</P>
<P>
   16. ``Washington D.C.'' (novel)
</P>
