<HEADLINE>
GO WILD FOR PRIDE OF PLACE SETTINGS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JUNE NAYLOR RODRIGUEZ 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Tree frogs on the dinner table? Crouton-size diamonds scattered
