<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-03 22:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6944 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LEWINSKY-INTERVIEW2-B     03-03 1374
